		<td class="salutationRight">Winchester, Tuesday 31st August, 1756.</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
</div>
<p></p>
</div>
<div class="docbody">
<div class="opener">
<table class="password"><tr>
		<td class="parole">Parole: Damascus.</td>
		<td class="csigns"></td>
	      </tr></table>
<table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">Winchester, Wednesday 1st September, 1756.</td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
</div>
<p>The General court martial to sit, according to the Order of the 29th augustEnsign Milner to sit in the room of Lieutenant BlaggThey are to try all Prisoners that be brought before them.</p>
</div>
